songs.title: My Type [Claws Remix]
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Ah, yeah
This is our time, ladies
Hennessy on my lips, take a little sip
Privacy on the door, I'ma make the sh- grip
We finna run this town
(Icy)

[Chorus]
Rich hitta, eight-figure, that’s my type
That's my type, that's my type
Eight-inch big, ooh, that’s good pipe
Bad chick, I'ma ride it right all night
Rich hitta, eight-figure, that's my type
That's my type, that's my type
Eight-inch big, ooh, that's good pipe
That's my type, that's my type

[Post-Chorus]
New wrist, new whip, ride around dipped
I can see why, all these basic chicks pissed

[Verse 1]
Big talk, big claws, breakin laws
Got a bag full of money, to the bank, Santa Claus
Yeah, rich chick in Palmetto
Heels like my nails, long, wear stiletto
Woo, g-gang, g-strings
Riding with my clique we the baddest in the game
Des, Jenny, V, Polly and Ann
Catch a tan on the sand
Count a couple grand

[Pre-Chorus]
Hennessy on my lips, take a little sip
Privacy on the door, I’ma make the sh- grip

[Chorus]
Rich hitta, eight-figure, that’s my type
That's my type, that’s my type
Eight-inch big, ooh, that's good pipe
Bad chick, I'ma ride it right all night
Rich hitta, eight-figure, that's my type
That’s my type, that's my type
Eight-inch big, ooh, that's good pipe
That's my type, that's my type

[Post-Chorus]
New wrist, new whip, ride around dipped
I can see why, all these basic chicks pissed

[Verse 2]
Five-star clique (clique)
Five-star chicks (chicks)
Iced-out wrist, iced-out tips
Catch an attitude girl, put my nail in your coffin
Riding with my crew, and you know we get it poppin'
Pop, pop, poppin' it off
Acetone on my money, call it washing it off
Get it, flip it, count it, deposit
Don't care about your man
We just care about his wallet

[Pre-Chorus]
Hennessy on my lips, take a little sip
Privacy on the door, I'ma make the sh- grip

[Chorus]
Rich hitta, eight-figure, that's my type
That's my type, that's my type
Eight-inch big, ooh, that's good pipe
That's my type, that's my type
